snippet.title: Amber Rose Takes Part In The Slut Walk & 50 Cent’s rivalry with Diddy Continues
snippet.description:
Please watch: "J. Prince Talks Drake & Pusha T Beef, Rap-A-Lot Records, & New Book | Soulful Sundays" 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lcyMS4tY1UI --~--
First, Amber Rose uses her time at the Slut Walk in Los Angeles to address Wiz Khalifa and Kanye West. Second, 50 Cent clowns Diddy again during a promotional run for Effen vodka. Last, T-Wayne stops by the DXHQ to talk the recently released “Nasty Freestyle” remix video. 

Shot & Edited By: Valerie Sakmary (@valeriexrose) & 
Written & Hosted By: Ural Garrett (@uralg)
